# -------------------------------------------------
# Generated per-machine
# -------------------------------------------------
# The launcher exe + _internal/ are a PyInstaller onedir pair, rebuilt by
# setup.bat (and by the in-app updater when missing post-pull). They were
# previously tracked, but local rebuilds collided with `git pull` whenever
# a commit also touched the exe — see CLAUDE.md section 2 rule 8.
CNA Web App.exe
_internal/
CODE - do not open/installer/CNA Web App.spec
*.lnk
installer-output/
CODE - do not open/installer/build/
CODE - do not open/installer/dist/
CODE - do not open/.last_update_check
CODE - do not open/.update_available
CODE - do not open/.migrated_to_azure
CODE - do not open/.azure_authed
CODE - do not open/favorites.json
CODE - do not open/ta_account_favorites.json
CODE - do not open/user_profile_cache.json

